<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来的几个星期，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们愉快地开始了他们的户外探险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>既然来到了乡下，他们就不用去上学了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈大部分时间都在房间里写故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为现在家里穷，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她要靠写故事赚钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们仍然有好看的衣服和足够的食物，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以他们并不在意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们没有忘记爸爸，只是不再提起他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们知道说起爸爸会让妈妈伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>六月的时候，连下了三天雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天气很冷，没有人出门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，他们来到妈妈的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以生火吗？” 鲍比问，“太冷了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，鲍比，煤太贵了。” 妈妈回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我们只需要一点点煤！” 鲍比恳求说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们买不起！” 妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去玩吧。我很忙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈总是很忙。” 菲利斯小声对彼得说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在思考。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>喝完茶，彼得对姐妹们说：“我有一个主意。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么主意？” 鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不告诉你。” 彼得回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。” 鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就别告诉我们。” 菲利斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们才不在乎呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得生气地说：“我不告诉你们是有原因的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的想法可能是错的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“错的事就不要去做！” 鲍比回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不。” 彼得说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定要做！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有的人会觉得是错的，但我不这么觉得。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果妈妈问我去了哪里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就告诉她我在玩儿一个叫‘挖煤’的游戏。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两天后，彼得说：“快来， 带上婴儿车！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>之前，孩子们在房后的库房里，看到一辆婴儿车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女孩儿们推着车，跟着彼得来到火车站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在火车站旁的山坡上，有一小堆煤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我刚刚找到这些煤。” 彼得说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“帮我运回家吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比、彼得和菲利斯用婴儿车搬了三趟才搬完。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把煤倒在后门旁边的煤堆里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>之后，彼得一个人出去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他回来的时候身上脏兮兮的，看上去很神秘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得每天晚上都出去，孩子们没有告诉任何人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个星期后，维尼夫人说煤好像变多了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们很开心——他们忘了彼得可能做了错事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个安静的夜晚，火车站站长躲在暗处，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着彼得爬上煤堆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抓住你了，小偷！” 站长大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抓着彼得的夹克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跟我去警察局！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是小偷！”彼得说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他的声音在发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“警察局？” 另一个声音说，是鲍比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比和菲利斯从黑暗里走出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们也有错。” 鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>站长看着他们，“ 我认识你们！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们住在山坡上的白房子里，为什么偷煤？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不觉得是偷，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里的煤太多了。” 彼得说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈说，我们太穷了，不能生火。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>站长想了想，说：“这次就算了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是要记住，这是火车站的煤，拿走就是偷。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们知道，站长说得对。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>